title: Why Are the Giants and Jets Still Considered Underdogs?
description: Bookmakers aren’t yet sold on the teams, despite winning records and solid upsets. Their distrust comes down to close games and weak schedules.
dc:creator: Victor Mather
media:credit: AJ Mast for the New York Times
media:description: The rookie running back Breece Hall has made an impact early in the Jets’ season.
